41
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:43,350
Don't worry about me.

42
00:03:43,350 --> 00:03:43,920
I mean.

43
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:46,570
Who's worrying about you?

44
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:47,480
Who do you think you are?

45
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:48,940
Is this your house?

46
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,350
Do you think you can come and go as you please?

47
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:52,120
I'm here to spend the holidays with you.

48
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:52,940
What holidays?

49
00:03:52,940 --> 00:03:54,030
The Lantern Festival!

50
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,340
Have you forgotten

51
00:03:55,340 --> 00:03:55,990
that it's the fifteenth of the first lunar month?

52
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:57,700
No, I haven't.

53
00:03:57,930 --> 00:03:59,360
but I don't remember agreeing to spend it with you.

54
00:03:59,510 --> 00:03:59,980
Hey.

55
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:00,990
Have you forgotten?

56
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:01,900
It was the fifth or the sixth of the New Year.

57
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,630
And you said you wanted to spend the holidays with me.

58
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:05,340
I was talking about that one particular day,

59
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:06,780
not today.

60
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:08,390
We already spent that day together.

61
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:09,220
Why not today?

62
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:10,430
We already spent that day together then.

63
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:11,860
Why must we be together today?

64
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:13,290
That's because we spent that day together.

65
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:15,820
Don't quarrel with me.

66
00:04:16,350 --> 00:04:17,100
Just get out of here.

67
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,910
How can you do this to me?

68
00:04:19,910 --> 00:04:21,730
I even canceled my gig at the temple fair for this.

69
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,420
The wage today is supposed to be doubled!

70
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:25,610
I made sacrifice for you!

71
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:28,120
So you're saying I have something to do with you quitting your job?

72
00:04:28,460 --> 00:04:29,740
Did I force you to quit?

73
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:30,880
I mean,

74
00:04:31,090 --> 00:04:32,540
I bought glutinous balls here to celebrate.

75
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:34,190
It's gonna be a waste if we don't eat them together.

76
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:35,900
Where are you planing to go during the New Year?

77
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:37,150
-Hey. -Come on.

78
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:41,350
Hurry and cook those glutinous rice balls.

79
00:04:41,420 --> 00:04:42,420
Leave once you're done eating.

80
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:43,080
Roger.

81
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,730
Is it that delicious?

82
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:54,880
It's so sweet.

83
00:04:54,909 --> 00:04:55,510
Don't you think it's too sweet?

84
00:04:55,810 --> 00:04:56,420
Not at all.

85
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,690
When I was a child, I loved eating glutinous rice balls.

86
00:04:57,909 --> 00:04:59,390
Back then, my grandmother used to make handmade glutinous rice balls,

87
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:00,670
and they tasted much better than the ones available elsewhere.

88
00:05:02,890 --> 00:05:04,260
Let's hang out in the afternoon.

89
00:05:04,670 --> 00:05:05,160
Nope.

90
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:07,780
Fine.

91
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:08,510
I'll entertain myself.

92
00:05:09,420 --> 00:05:11,060
What's so fun about being alone?

93
00:05:12,270 --> 00:05:13,420
