101
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:34,790
Fine.

102
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:36,280
I'll hang out with you.

103
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:38,040
Joyrides, hitting on girls,

104
00:05:38,180 --> 00:05:38,750
