105
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:39,950
Pick whatever you want.

106
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:41,360
I'll pay.

107
00:05:46,650 --> 00:05:47,780
Wow, there are so many people here.

108
00:05:48,730 --> 00:05:49,890
Please make way. Make way.

109
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:51,300
Hey!

110
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,630
I don't get it.

111
00:05:53,870 --> 00:05:55,620
You're here all the time.

112
00:05:56,010 --> 00:05:57,560
