113
00:05:57,980 --> 00:05:59,460
Indeed, I'm here all the time.

114
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:00,430
But I never truly spent my time here.

115
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:02,750
When I was dancing and performing on stage,

116
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:03,940
my biggest wish was

117
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:05,380
joining the crowd down there

118
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:05,990
enjoying the show,

119
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,840
and buying some stuff.

120
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:07,700
It would be so much fun.

121
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,600
Come here.

122
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,780
Such a loser.

123
00:06:24,020 --> 00:06:24,750
It's so fun!

124
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:29,630
Hit it.

125
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:50,620
This is for you.

126
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:56,060
Wow.

127
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:58,350
I bought it for 47,000 yuan.

128
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,390
If you want to sell it,

129
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:01,660
