130
00:07:02,980 --> 00:07:04,260
What does your family do for a living?

131
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:05,780
Why are you so rich?

132
00:07:06,550 --> 00:07:07,590
It's not your business.

133
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:12,060
Who's richer?

134
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:12,820
You or Xia Yao?

135
00:07:16,290 --> 00:07:18,010
My family can't be compared to his.

136
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:19,270
What?

137
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:20,150
Then,

138
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:21,710
why does Xia Yao

139
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:23,090
