140
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:25,790
Some things can't be measured by money.

141
00:07:27,090 --> 00:07:27,580
I'd rather

142
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:29,430
grovel and lick someone else's boots

143
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:30,780
