149
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:42,630
Give it to me.

150
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,540
My gosh, it really is gold!

151
00:07:43,540 --> 00:07:44,280
I'm taking it back.

152
00:07:44,470 --> 00:07:45,180
I won't give it to you.

153
00:07:45,180 --> 00:07:46,020
Hey, you said it's a gift for me.

154
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,180
How can you take it back?

155
00:07:48,220 --> 00:07:49,950
Because I've never seen someone looks so jobless as you do.

156
