161
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,540
Come and take a look.

162
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,510
Five yuan for each.

163
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,670
Hey, how about 10 yuan for three of this?

164
00:08:17,340 --> 00:08:18,220
Take one.

165
00:08:18,620 --> 00:08:20,000
I'll give you a discount, don't go.

166
