Childish.

185
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:57,380
Ten yuan for three of this.

186
00:08:58,110 --> 00:08:59,150
Wow, let's get one.

187
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:00,740
I'll give you a discount. Don't go.

188
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:03,750
Hey, take a look. It's cheap here.

189
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:05,500
Hey.

190
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:06,140
Come and have a look.

191
00:09:06,310 --> 00:09:07,250
Do you want some cotton candy?

192
00:09:07,810 --> 00:09:08,570
Yeah! Sure!

193
00:09:08,860 --> 00:09:09,670
I want some!

194
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:14,670
