196
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,740
I want to have this mushroom plushie!

197
00:09:19,350 --> 00:09:21,230
Come and have a look.

198
00:09:21,230 --> 00:09:21,740
Sir,

199
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:22,950
