225
00:11:20,470 --> 00:11:20,780
Come.

226
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:21,390
Come on in!

227
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:22,420
Get in.

228
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:23,190
Mom!

229
00:11:23,190 --> 00:11:23,900
