234
00:11:27,990 --> 00:11:28,830
Am I embarrassing you?

235
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:29,760
Look at what you have done.

236
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:31,310
Do I need to think about how you feel right now?

237
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:31,930
Auntie.

238
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:33,380
I asked Xia Yao come over.

239
00:11:33,630 --> 00:11:34,920
I had a family emergency and needed his help.

240
00:11:35,050 --> 00:11:36,010
It's my fault that

241
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:36,940
