242
00:11:36,940 --> 00:11:38,820
Couldn't he tell me first?

243
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,640
A call wouldn't take up much of your time!

244
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:42,710
He's intentionally trying to annoy us,

245
00:11:42,710 --> 00:11:44,230
-refusing to go to the blind date! I'll give you a lesson! -Blind date?

246
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:44,660
I'll hit...

247
00:11:46,190 --> 00:11:46,740
Auntie.

248
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:48,140
I made him come over.

249
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:48,970
At the time,

250
00:11:49,030 --> 00:11:50,710
he called me to request a few extra days off,

251
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:52,200
and coincidentally I needed someone to help out urgently,

252
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:53,390
so I called him over temporarily.

253
00:11:53,780 --> 00:11:54,520
It was my fault that

254
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:55,970
he didn't inform you about this.

255
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:57,100
Mom.

256
00:11:57,180 --> 00:11:57,780
Look,

257
00:11:58,070 --> 00:11:59,420
I brought you some Harbin sausages.

258
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:00,780
His family made these themselves.

259
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:01,530
And this,

260
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:02,350
smoked meat.

261
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:04,560
Weren't you complaining that we didn't receive any this year?

262
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:05,970
He made these for you.

263
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:07,420
Smell it.

264
00:12:07,770 --> 00:12:08,800
It's definitely as good as the stuff we received.

265
00:12:12,990 --> 00:12:13,630
Yuan Zong,

266
00:12:13,970 --> 00:12:15,090
did you really make these yourself?

267
00:12:16,350 --> 00:12:16,940
Mom.

268
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:17,960
I even brought this back to you.

269
00:12:18,210 --> 00:12:20,040
The most authentic mountain delicacies from the northeast.

270
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:22,350
They're great for making soup and braising meat.

271
00:12:22,580 --> 00:12:23,870
I even brought back ginseng

272
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:24,640
and antlers.

273
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:26,170
All the best stuff from the northeast

274
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,460
are here.

275
00:12:28,130 --> 00:12:29,190
All right, all right.

276
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,300
Tell me

277
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:31,340
before you leave next time.

278
00:12:31,620 --> 00:12:32,900
If you pull this nonsense again,

279
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:34,320
