281
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:38,220
Yuan Zong.

282
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:38,770
Come here.

283
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:39,930
Have a seat.

284
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:41,090
Come and have a seat.

285
00:12:55,090 --> 00:12:55,980
Does your ear still hurt?

286
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:57,560
It doesn't,

287
00:12:57,820 --> 00:12:58,690
