00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:03,830
Alas,

291
00:13:04,380 --> 00:13:05,150
an old woman

292
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:05,780
like her is probably lonely.

293
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:10,130
What's up with that blind date thing?

294
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:12,900
During the New Year festival,

295
00:13:12,950 --> 00:13:14,640
my dad set up a blind date for me.

296
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:15,580
He wanted me to meet her.

297
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:17,220
Then?

298
00:13:19,170 --> 00:13:20,360
Nothing happened.

299
00:13:34,190 --> 00:13:34,830
Is it good?

300
00:13:37,540 --> 00:13:38,060
Hey,

301
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:39,090
did that guy

302
00:13:39,530 --> 00:13:40,970
really make these smoked meat?

303
00:13:42,420 --> 00:13:43,260
Wow,

304
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:44,270
he doesn't seem like

305
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:45,860
he can cook.

306
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:48,320
Then, you're totally wrong.

307
00:13:49,220 --> 00:13:50,350
Not only can he cook,

308
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:52,150
but he's also quite the chef.

309
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:54,750
That sticky rice lotus root dish you often praise,

310
00:13:56,020 --> 00:13:57,360
well, it wasn't something I bought

311
00:13:57,490 --> 00:13:58,550
He actually made it himself.

312
00:13:58,890 --> 00:13:59,630
Really?

313
00:13:59,730 --> 00:14:00,770
That's impressive, isn't it?

314
00:14:01,380 --> 00:14:02,110
Yeah, duh!

315
00:14:03,990 --> 00:14:05,910
What a good boy.

316
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:08,460
If any girl can marry him,

317
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:10,120
she must be very lucky.

318
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,600
What are you laughing at?

319
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:16,480
You should learn from him.

320
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:34,610
The number you dialed is busy now.

321
00:14:35,830 --> 00:14:36,610
[Xuan Dayu]

322
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:44,420
The number you have called is busy now.

323
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:46,490
Weird.

324
00:14:47,230 --> 00:14:48,650
Why can't I get through to his phone?

325
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:51,430
Where is this guy?

326
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:00,380
[Peng Ze]

327
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:05,670
What's up, Yao?

328
00:15:05,980 --> 00:15:06,450
Hey,

329
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:09,410
do you know where Dayu is?

330
00:15:09,730 --> 00:15:10,530
I don't know.

331
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:12,430
I haven't been in touch with him for a long time.

332
00:15:12,990 --> 00:15:13,500
What's the matter?

333
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:15,020
I can ask around

334
00:15:15,220 --> 00:15:16,190
if you're looking for him.

335
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:16,960
It's fine.

336
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:18,040
I'll do it myself.

337
00:15:19,540 --> 00:15:19,940
Okay.

338
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:50,430
What brings you here?

339
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,470
I've been looking for you for quite a few days.

340
00:16:00,010 --> 00:16:01,330
Why didn't you pick up my calls?

341
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,080
I also spent days looking for you.

342
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:04,990
Did you pick up my calls?

343
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,270
I was in the northeast back then.

344
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:08,610
Don't even mention about that.

345
00:16:09,060 --> 00:16:09,750
I don't want to hear it.

346
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:13,460
You're mad now, huh?

347
00:16:14,610 --> 00:16:15,640
You broke my heart.

348
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:16,670
So I have erased all my longing.

349
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:18,590
Do you have to be that dramatic?

350
00:16:19,380 --> 00:16:20,800
It's just that I didn't pick up

351
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,060
your calls or chat with you.

352
00:16:22,620 --> 00:16:23,790
Xia Yao, listen up.

353
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:26,140
It's not just about the phone calls.

354
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:27,920
What place do I hold in your heart?

355
00:16:28,250 --> 00:16:29,870
And how much significance do you have in mine?

356
00:16:30,350 --> 00:16:31,390
You should think about it.

357
00:16:32,380 --> 00:16:33,830
You've been hiding all kinds of secrets.

358
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:35,400
You should be well aware of that.

359
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:35,220
Rich Xuan!

360
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:38,220
Mr. Xuan!

361
00:17:39,060 --> 00:17:40,020
Xuan, the rich guy!

362
00:17:40,940 --> 00:17:41,500
Sir!

363
00:17:43,780 --> 00:17:44,430
What are you doing here?

364
00:17:45,170 --> 00:17:47,270
I went to look for a famous store selling sour and spicy noodles.

365
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:48,590
The two bowls I ate yesterday weren't enough,

366
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:49,860
so I went to buy more today.

367
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:51,270
I brought them here for you to try.

368
00:17:52,660 --> 00:17:53,640
Try it.

369
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:55,550
I guarantee that it's spicy, sour, and flavorful.

370
00:17:55,970 --> 00:17:57,050
If you like rich tastes,

371
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,400
I have two extra packets of vinegar.

372
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:03,370
Piss off!
